                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.001 Chiang Kai-shek/12</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum of Conversation, by the Secretary of State</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-11-22">November 22,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Chinese Ambassador called under instructions of General Chiang Kai-shek to
                    extend to me the most hearty and sincere congratulations of the Generalissimo
                    for my aid to China at Moscow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>C[<hi rend="smallcaps">ordell</hi>] H[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                        >ull</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
